{"tid":2123970,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我們真的失守了！  公共醫療醫生協會會長 - 馬仲儀","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T15:09:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b45ee445da4cbdabacacba926188111c4aaa6244","tid":2123970,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/BUQ4O6H5BZNAHCJS7FUZODR6ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FBUQ4O6H5BZNAHCJS7FUZODR6ZU%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=f2f73e87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FBUQ4O6H5BZNAHCJS7FUZODR6ZU%2F&h=c149a947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/BUQ4O6H5BZNAHCJS7FUZODR6ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n我們真的失守了！ <br />\n公共醫療醫生協會會長 - 馬仲儀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FF49OQEOrfWUqHTGPsESMs1Coko=/1487x724/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ETQP4GCAWZ4B2KAEKJ5JMDOSBY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFF49OQEOrfWUqHTGPsESMs1Coko%3D%2F1487x724%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FETQP4GCAWZ4B2KAEKJ5JMDOSBY.gif&h=46bbd0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年6月是香港最後的平靜日子&mdash;&mdash;五、六月時，大家還在盼望連續28天零本地感染；七月首兩星期，整個社會在政治和公共衞生上已變得天昏地暗。7月5日那個星期開始，本地感染個案每天雙位數上升，到了現在單日數字過百，整體感染人數也超越了SARS。你可以說數字是冰冷的，那便看看那些找不到感染源頭的個案，看看那些如繁星亂墜的十八區感染個案分佈地圖，看看那琳琅滿目的多人聚餐感染群組。<br />\n<br />\n今波疫情有幾個特點。第一是社區感染者眾，而且散落各區。第二，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。看似再難避免。無奈地，恒常的服務再一次被叫停，我們脆弱的醫療系統再一次被癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靈活運用公私資源仍有餘力<br />\n<br />\n控制疫情，應先堵截源頭，任憑你再口硬，專家們已清楚說明，今波疫情由豁免檢疫人士傳入。所有來港人士早應先進行病毒測試，等待結果期間需在特定地方隔離居住。談引致社區傳播的責任，市民和政府應各佔一半。政府為了盡快讓飲食和旅遊業走出困境，過度放寬了餐廳和大型主題樂園的限制。市民亦鬆懈下來，不斷參加社交聚會飲宴，把握脫下口罩的機會。疫症爆發後，政府再次限制餐廳經營，也加強了強制戴口罩的規定，但能否控制社區傳播還看市民的公德心。<br />\n<br />\n大家經常問公立醫院會不會「爆煲」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n倘若我們真的敗於新冠肺炎之下，。。。。。。。。。。。見證現時政府的施政更令人絕望。<br />\n<br />\n馬仲儀<br />\n公共醫療醫生協會會長"},{"pid":"cda19263917db7d109352044aef7fdbddd5b767b","tid":2123970,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"慶回歸.gif"},{"pid":"1e8cd606716f928e779b4a57a2b92743c5026fa7","tid":2123970,"uid":76577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"要幫手推啦<br />\n我個藍絲老豆岩岩問我佢係乜水<br />\n仲話佢係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">支持良心醫護！</span>"},{"pid":"0bb16a496a1c69a79d110b553149c8da7bb001e7","tid":2123970,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003019a5b8df0484b87a3a27aab0a4ccc0f1c83e","tid":2123970,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"要怪就怪林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢引入病毒 主持攬炒"}]}